title: Silent Decay - Complet Discography
description:
Silent Decay was a modern metal band from Munich. Originally the band started with a mixture of Thrash Metal and Death Metal, built over time, but more and more modern elements from the fields of neo thrash, screamo or metalcore one.

This group does not play anymore, they stopped in 2010.

This is the complete discography that includes three single albums: 

2005 - World Of Lies 
2007 - The Creation Of Paint 
2009 - King Of The Death End Road
